                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Charleston</placeName>\n                                        <date>August 15<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1852</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Dear Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(4)\">During your<lb/> late stay in this city my mother\n                                        subscribed to a full <sic>sett</sic><lb/> of your “Prayer\n                                        Book for the whole year” which you<lb/> promised to forward\n                                        to her upon your return to <placeName>Phda.</placeName><lb/>\n                                        the same have not reached her yet.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The Holy days now approaching and having<lb/>\n                                        urgent use for them at those times, <sic>compells</sic> her\n                                        to<lb/> inform you that unless you forward the same in\n                                        time<lb/> for them to reach here one week before <add>ראש\n                                                  השנה</add> next<lb/> she will not consider herself\n                                        under obligation to receive<lb/> the same should they arrive\n                                        after that time, as she<lb/> would, in case of the\n                                        non-arrival of yours up to the<lb/> above mentioned time, be\n                                        compelled to supply herself<lb/> in this place   With great\n                                        respect I am</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(6)\">Your mst obd Srvt</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Maier Trust</persName>\n                              </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3x05xz8v/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
